{"word":"G4169 - ποῖος - poîos - poy'-os - What","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ποῖος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">poîos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">poy'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">What</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"புல், பூண்டு - பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"herbage, grass"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G4226 - ποῦ - poû - poo/4226\">G4226</a> and <a href=\"#/G3634 - οἷος - hoîos - hoy'-os/3634\">G3634</a>; individualizing interrogitive (of character) <i>what</i> sort of, or (of number) <i>which</i> one: - what (manner of), which.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}